Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.29,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.92,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:33.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:48.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:55.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:01:02.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:10.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:13.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:17.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:21.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:28.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:35.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:39.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:43.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:49.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:55.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:58.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go follow Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drat. Looks like they really\Ndon't know where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we strangle this Franky guy,\Nif he already spent the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now? Even if we wait for\Nhim here, he won't be back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Staying here talking won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the ship for now.\NWe left Nami-san alone there, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.34,0:02:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the thing with\NRobin-chan to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.63,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the issues with the ship, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say goodbye... to the Going Merry here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:07.91,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Big Fight under the Moon!\NThe Pirate Flag Flutters with Sorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp woke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can relax a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan isn't back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't worry us so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. To think that you marched\Nin by yourself... That was so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky that you didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think a little before you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because I'm so good-for-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really... I'm ashamed! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money was so crucial to\Nus and yet, I let it... I let it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold on a sec! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I get it, so let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... the huge amount of money we got,\Nafter all that we went through...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you should still be in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen to Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as I was afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the money won't come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we won't know for sure\Nuntil this Franky guy comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if we don't get it back,\Nwe still have the 100 million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's okay. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not okay about the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami...\N--Ah... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy... What about the ship?\NWhat about the Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we somehow have her repaired\Nwith that remaining 100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky that we can have her\Nrepaired in such a first-class shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order for her to be able to travel in\Nthe seas ahead, I'd like her to be stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want her to be repaired perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, does it look like those guys will\Nrepair her if we pay 100 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, about the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to get a new ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I made the\Ndecision without consulting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've already made my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry took good care of us,\Nbut our journey with her ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a look at the catalogue\Nthat Ice pops gave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While checking the ships in it, I noticed\Nthat there're quite a few kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we get a used one, 100 million will\Nallow us to buy a bigger ship than Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Wait a sec. You're taking\Nthe joke too far. That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Chopper took it seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what'll we do with our captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something to him, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... does that mean that we don't\Nhave enough money for the repair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I got that 200 million stolen by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,w-we're now short on money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's what's going on, right, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cost of a first-class shipyard\Nwould also be first-class, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why?! Spit it out! Are you\Ntrying to be considerate to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! It has nothing to do\Nwith that money being stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you saying stupid stuff\Nlike that we're gonna get a new ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What good will fighting do?\NCalm down and talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I calm down when he\Nstarts saying stupid stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This is an important matter.\NDon't get so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.83,0:07:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Usopp. You need\Nto rest, or you won't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I be quiet when our captain\Ncasually says we'll get a new ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not casual! I made the\Ndecision after agonizing over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What and how did you agonize over\Nto make this kind of decision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you talk about it\Nwhile waving this stupid thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, if it wasn't because we\Ngot our money stolen, then why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, why don't you say it?! Hey!\NWhy are you keeping quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not being considerate\Nto me, then don't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.44,0:07:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it! I won't accept it unless\NI hear good reason! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry can no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry can no longer be repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we do, she won't be fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I wouldn't say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship?! Are you talking about this\Nship that we're on board right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This ship will sink soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth. They told us at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that she can't\Neven reach the next island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really... She can't, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were persuaded by\Nstrangers you just met today
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and gave up just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because first-class\Nshipwrights told you that this is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you gave up just like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've traveled together all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it through all sorts\Nof waves and battles together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's our dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna abandon her in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how little this ship means to you, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't shout like that, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry, but step aside.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.63,0:09:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you make an accurate assessment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have a shipwright on this ship.\NThat's why we asked them to check her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! We don't have to\Nask those guys to fix her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll repair her, as I always have!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we've continued\Nto travel in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start now. Hey, help me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, we don't have enough lumber.\NI'll go buy some at the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're getting busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a shipwright, are you, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.89,0:10:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't trust irresponsible\Nshipwrights who easily give up on a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because it belongs to someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by taking advantage of\Ntheir position as craftsmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a lesson that we should\Nprotect our own ship by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never... give up on this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably got fooled by the shipwrights'\Nconvincing argument, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Luffy I know would've believed\Nin the strength of the Merry first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rather than buying those guys' sales talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a clear-cut answer that sounds
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like one made by an old man\Nwho understands everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you make a decision like that,\Nsuddenly acting all captain-like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I misjudged you, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec, Usopp! Luffy, too, first--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this, Nami!\NThis is something I decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't change my opinion.\NNo matter what you say now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're gonna get a new ship!\NWe'll say goodbye to the Merry here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! I won't allow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy! It's not like everyone\Ncan live looking ahead like you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave our wounded friend\Nhere and move on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! Even if she's a friend,\Nships and humans are different!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the same! Merry has\Nthe strength to live left in her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Considering how you are, aren't you\Nexcited thinking about the new ship\N--Hey, that's enough, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--while pretending to be concerned about Merry?!\N--You can't have a conversation\Nif you're worked up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think that you're the only\None who feels pain over this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone feels the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, there's no way you'd\Ndecide to get a new ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! If you dislike what I decide\Nthat much, then get off this--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot... What were you about to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down! Be careful about\Nwhat you say! Got that, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.01,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, Luffy. That's how\Nyou really feel, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna abandon the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you do that to me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and cut off useless friends\None after another and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna abandon the Merry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you do that to me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp. Don't say stupid stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking that I can't keep\Nup with your monstrous strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like today... I can't even watch over money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep causing you guys trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need weak friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... you're the man\Nwho'll be king of the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have to go that high up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking back, when I was about to sail out,\Nyou guys asked me to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about? Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all that's tying us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to travel together\Nwhen we have a difference of opinion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where're you going, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where I'm going is my own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you guys anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...leaving the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What're you doing, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to let him go like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Go after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come this far together.\NIs it okay to part like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is our precious friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy... You are the captain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't you saying anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! It shouldn't be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I can't go along with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to cause you trouble until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the ship\Nbelongs to you, the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So fight me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight a duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? Er, hey... what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At 10 o'clock tonight, I'll come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll fight a duel over the Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you and take the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the end of the bond\Nbetween you guys and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?! Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to fight\Na duel with your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give it a little time,\Nyou two will cool down, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, too. He just got flared up\Nbecause things were moving quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've come this far, we can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can apologize to him and talk it over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said... it's no longer possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp isn't stupid enough to risk\Nhis life under the influence of anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if talking it over\Nwould change his opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get it, leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying, the Franky Family\Ncame here this afternoon, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you beat them\Nall up beyond recovery then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had, Usopp wouldn't have\Nbeen attacked and felt guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, instead of going shopping,\Nyou should've stayed and fought them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to get necessary food as your cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop fighting at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been enough fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight over what's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...! But this idiot is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper... Didn't you... go follow Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to continue treating his wounds,\Nbut he turned me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got a place to stay in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.85,0:19:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "You and I are no longer friends,\Nso go back to the ship!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that fun time up until this\Nmorning seems like a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something is happening\Nto Robin on top of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like... the gang is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I somehow feel restless tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 10 o'clock, the promised time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, don't leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There he is!\N--Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.16,0:21:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you didn't get cold feet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be sure you're not going\Nto regret this, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the duel you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You'd better fight seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the tables on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already figured out how to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.11,0:22:26.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:32.24,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.24,0:22:34.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:43.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:46.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:49.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:51.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:54.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:57.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:00.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.52,0:23:06.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:11.82,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.41,0:23:19.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. It's ridiculous for friends to fight a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once what we protect becomes\Ndifferent, we're no longer friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. Luffy, you restrain yourself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely because we're all friends,\Nbe prepared and watch quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy vs. Usopp! Collision of Two Men's Pride"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
